description: Section 73 application to vary Condition 1 (Development in accordance with approved plans) of planning permission reference No. 2008/1753 dated 8 September 2010 comprising of a reduction in Class B1 (a-c) use of 7,871 sq m to 7,021 sq m GEA [7,543 sq m to 5,995 sq m GIA] and a revised residential mix of accommodation comprising of 108 X 1-bed, 153 X 2-bed, 57 X 3-bed, 8 X 4-bed and 1 X 5-bed.
